reviews.review_text:
hottest is correct... Killer show...and also one of the most sweltering hot nights as well....
Good 'ol days....and nights!
TR
This was epic! Dancin' set the tone, while Gloria wrapped it up nicely. Hard to believe almost 26 years ago.

Drug Busts This is one of the first shows where there were MAJOR drug busts. They had DEA on top of the buildings with binoculars pointing out people on the ground. There were over 200 arrests. Listen to Jerry howl during High Time."I'm having a HARD time, living the good life..." Gloria was in recognition of Hurricane Gloria brewing outside and 11/04 Richmond flooded.  Amazing show one of my favorites of all time. This sounds great especially for this coliseum
